⸻

🧩 SAFE STATS UPDATE PIPELINE

⸻

Step 1: Replica test
	•	Run ANALYZE on replica

⸻

Step 2: Compare plans

EXPLAIN ANALYZE


⸻

Step 3: Validate latency

