🎯 FINAL TAKEAWAY

⸻

✅ YES — problem exists in ALL DBs

DB	Risk	Control
SQL Server	High	Query Store
Oracle	High	Plan Baselines
Postgres	Medium	Stats tuning
RDS Postgres	Medium	Parameter tuning


⸻

✅ BEST DEFENSE
	•	Controlled stats updates
	•	Plan monitoring
	•	Replica validation
	•	Ability to force plan

